-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Libraries:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ast - conver string to dict
cryptography.fernet - crypt and decrypt messages
json - convert string to dict
os - run scripts
paramiko - ssh connections for transfering client scirpt to remote machine
platform - get information about OS on client
psutil - getting inromation from hosts
sqlite3 - database creation and storing data
smtplib - send message about problems on host
uptime - get machine uptime
xmltodict - convert xml to dict for simplest processing it to db
xml.etree.ElementTree as ET - parsing xml

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Components
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
client.py - uses for getting information from hosts and encrypt it with fernet
runner.py - script for running project, uses client.py and server.py
server.py - communicate with DB and client for parsing data from xml, db, send messages for clients
            and etc
settings.py - storing settings for project